Consider the following C function.
<pre><code class="c">int fun ( int n ) {
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; int x = 1, k ;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; if ( n == 1) return x ;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for( k = 1 ; k &lt; n ; ++ k )
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; x = x + fun( k ) * fun( n - k ) ;
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return x ;
<br>}</code></pre>
